### List tasks
GET http://localhost:3000/tasks HTTP/1.1

### Filter tasks by name
GET http://localhost:3000/tasks?name=project HTTP/1.1

### Filter tasks by due date range
GET http://localhost:3000/tasks?dueDateFrom=2025-11-01T00:00:00Z&dueDateTo=2025-12-31T23:59:59Z HTTP/1.1

### Filter tasks by name and due date
GET http://localhost:3000/tasks?name=setup&dueDateFrom=2025-11-01T00:00:00Z&dueDateTo=2025-12-31T23:59:59Z HTTP/1.1


### Get task by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/tasks/69173d2072c6c9ea34d55873 HTTP/1.1

### Create a new task
POST http://localhost:3000/tasks HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Write API tests",
  "description": "Create comprehensive tests for all endpoints",
  "dueDate": "2025-12-15T23:59:59Z",
  "completed": false
}

### Update a task
PUT http://localhost:3000/tasks/69173d2072c6c9ea34d55873 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Complete project setup",
  "description": "MongoDB and Task model completed successfully",
  "dueDate": "2025-11-30T23:59:59Z",
  "completed": true
}

### Delete a task
DELETE http://localhost:3000/tasks/69173d2072c6c9ea34d55873 HTTP/1.1